{"tid":93343,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「日語撚」初學日文求教","createTime":"2017-01-24T10:54:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-01T10:46:39.000Z","uid":60582,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"128f216d76c9443496eb64d252f99c762fb3794e","tid":93343,"uid":60582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T10:54:28.000Z","msg":"小弟準備3月報班學日文，聽人講事前自學左先會好d，岩岩係書局買左本由五十音基礎教起既書。<br />\n<br />\n我想問除左睇書之外仲有冇咩方法可以易上手同做好準備？另外五十音有咩方法可以好記d？求巴絲們指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce992be03e02706e44a924dbe0565042a5cfe2e3","tid":93343,"uid":3436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T11:30:55.000Z","msg":"罰抄咁抄 不斷抄<br />\n搵d 免費50音app 通常有d 測驗做<br />\n先搞掂平假名 有信心先開片假名<br />\n千祈唔好兩樣打孖上<br />\n熟既程度要用英文字母一樣 聽音/見字都立刻link 得埋"},{"pid":"08f0f0bf2d4982a84999c64b08b7850cb32565fa","tid":93343,"uid":53911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T11:32:13.000Z","msg":"你問得黎不如即刻開始背好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33d8f3082b63c745d47f732e9675760a3c4fb638","tid":93343,"uid":33534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T11:34:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>罰抄咁抄 不斷抄<br />\n搵d 免費50音app 通常有d 測驗做<br />\n先搞掂平假名 有信心先開片假名<br />\n千祈唔好兩樣打孖上<br />\n熟既程度要用英文字母一樣 聽音/見字都立刻link 得埋</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n學到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6266a0425865549ae3ac1ef12c93e0711caccaf","tid":93343,"uid":516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T11:35:35.000Z","msg":"上網玩下個50音練習器，玩兩野就記得啦"},{"pid":"3f2a91260dae8a7f6747edc3e00ffaeb497be8c0","tid":93343,"uid":60582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T11:36:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你問得黎不如即刻開始背好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n背都有方法嫁嘛，始終第一次學英文國語以外既外語，想睇下有冇特別易記既方式法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3c4f145f12e2dbe94f12185621b1910bdfd28db","tid":93343,"uid":60582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T11:37:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>罰抄咁抄 不斷抄<br />\n搵d 免費50音app 通常有d 測驗做<br />\n先搞掂平假名 有信心先開片假名<br />\n千祈唔好兩樣打孖上<br />\n熟既程度要用英文字母一樣 聽音/見字都立刻link 得埋</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔該哂你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />學到野 即刻dl app先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76aa7b53fb8b6269854202b3e829fe81ba9f5d52","tid":93343,"uid":3818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T11:37:55.000Z","msg":"罸抄最易記啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d62336db23fd7df72c6472f274774ed8cd6edb04","tid":93343,"uid":1169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T11:46:09.000Z","msg":"唔需要死抄死記 咁反而冇乜效 自然記先係最好<br />\n見到有個基本印象 望到知係乜就ok<br />\n要load一陣都冇所謂 見到唔記得咪查番表 越學會越熟<br />\n我個人就對住日文歌詞一路聽<br />\n不出一兩個月已經記得九成 完全冇抄過/比過effort"},{"pid":"1eddf216065c8d38a5dd10b65f5abd74fc2c5d45","tid":93343,"uid":1169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T11:48:35.000Z","msg":"日後啲生字仲難搞過五十音<br />\n都係用類似方法記<br />\n咪住個list抄真係冇乜效率<br />\n順其自然 多用多諗 自然會記得<br />\n純粹個人睇法 希望幫到你"},{"pid":"503b696790459f3bd9c2a880ad4911ecbbdd700e","tid":93343,"uid":45551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T11:50:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日後啲生字仲難搞過五十音<br />\n都係用類似方法記<br />\n咪住個list抄真係冇乜效率<br />\n順其自然 多用多諗 自然會記得<br />\n純粹個人睇法 希望幫到你</blockquote><br />\n學語言 本來就係多用多諗 就得<br />\n識番個架妹就得"},{"pid":"6750d4ffe35f04c44ae8b9fa88ae36451a6abfe3","tid":93343,"uid":48428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T11:57:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>日後啲生字仲難搞過五十音<br />\n都係用類似方法記<br />\n咪住個list抄真係冇乜效率<br />\n順其自然 多用多諗 自然會記得<br />\n純粹個人睇法 希望幫到你</blockquote><br />\n學語言 本來就係多用多諗 就得<br />\n識番個架妹就得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我就係想識架妹先學日文<br />\n你叫我識個黎學<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54aa8b32b28f78b84fe3c69023487f10a3300b5a","tid":93343,"uid":55732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T12:33:30.000Z","msg":"Practice makes perfect<br />\n背默係辛苦啲，但有佢效用<br />\n<br />\n再遲啲嘗試下多睇多用<br />\n例如睇住歌詞網唱歌<br />\n甚至plan下自由行去日本，上日文網站搵旅行資料<br />\n都有啲幫助"},{"pid":"030ec9636825fed802934957dbee2a7d60c97f9e","tid":93343,"uid":2023,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T10:42:06.000Z","msg":"出面學哂錢哂時間，教得好慢傢<br />\n比我教，我收得貴出面少少但進度快幾倍<br />\n你可以用起底功能search下我點解要教日文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nTelegram 搵我傾<br />\n@abcccccccc"},{"pid":"e1bb87f119d73efdec09ccf568729412223e094a","tid":93343,"uid":57646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T10:46:39.000Z","msg":"三月？Mr.Yau?"}]}